K10D0145=D0847_H0100:517b-17: kun ran gtsang dang aa ti mukta 'bebs //
K10D0145=D0847_H0100:517b-18: gling gzhan rnams na'ang sna tshogs char pa 'bebs //
K10D0145=D0847_H0100:517b-19: 'dzam bu'i gling du chu gsal dang ba yi //
K10D0145=D0847_H0100:517b-20: char rnams chos bzhin phra ba'i rgyun du 'bebs //
K10D0145=D0847_H0100:517b-21: me tog 'bras bu sman dang spos dang shing //
K10D0145=D0847_H0100:517b-22: lo tog bde byed 'jig rten rnams su skyed //
K10D0145=D0847_H0100:517b-23: de ltar sprin bkod bsam gyis mi khyab dang //
K10D0145=D0847_H0100:517b-24: glog 'byin 'brug sgrog bkod pa'i char 'bebs kyang //
K10D0145=D0847_H0100:517b-25: gnas nas mi g-yo rnam par rtog pa med //
K10D0145=D0847_H0100:517b-26: klu yi rnam 'phrul de ltar bsam mi khyab //
K10D0145=D0847_H0100:517b-27: rgya mtsho'i chu na gnas pa de ltar yang //
K10D0145=D0847_H0100:517b-28: klu yi rnam 'phrul bsam yas ston byed na //
K10D0145=D0847_H0100:518a-2: rnam 'phrul mtha' yas ci phyir ston mi byed //
K10D0145=D0847_H0100:518a-3: bag tsam smos pa'i dpe tshul 'di dag gis //
K10D0145=D0847_H0100:518a-4: skyes chen de dag rnams kyis brjod pa byas //
K10D0145=D0847_H0100:518a-5: dpa' bo de dag dpe rnams kun dang bral //
K10D0145=D0847_H0100:518a-6: de dag 'di 'dra'i rnam thar dbang sgyur ro //
K10D0145=D0847_H0100:518a-7: blo gros dam pa blo gros rgya chen ldan //
K10D0145=D0847_H0100:518a-8: ma nor blo gros mtha' yas blo gros can //
K10D0145=D0847_H0100:518a-9: ye shes mchog ldan khyad par blo can gyi //
K10D0145=D0847_H0100:518a-10: rnam thar mchog rnams 'di dag rnams kyis spyad //
K10D0145=D0847_H0100:518a-11: rnam thar dam pa 'di dag sus thos nas //
K10D0145=D0847_H0100:518a-12: yid ches 'dzin cing 'jig rten sgrog byed pa //
K10D0145=D0847_H0100:518a-13: de dag ngo mtshar rmad byung chos ldan de //
K10D0145=D0847_H0100:518a-14: de dag dka' byed mi yi 'jig rten na //
K10D0145=D0847_H0100:518a-15: 'di 'dra chos 'dir gang dag dad gyur pa //
K10D0145=D0847_H0100:518a-16: sems can so so'i skye bo'i tshogs na dkon; ;gang dag dge bsags bsod nams byas gyur pa //
K10D0145=D0847_H0100:518a-17: de dag rgyu yi stobs kyis 'di la dad //
K10D0145=D0847_H0100:518a-18: gang dag nyan thos theg la'ang yid ches pa'i //
K10D0145=D0847_H0100:518a-19: mi dag mi yi 'jig rten rnams na nyung //
K10D0145=D0847_H0100:518a-20: de bas rkyen gyi theg par rab tu nyung //
K10D0145=D0847_H0100:518a-21: theg pa chen por de dag de bas nyung //
K10D0145=D0847_H0100:518a-22: theg pa che la zhugs pa de dkon te //
K10D0145=D0847_H0100:518a-23: gang dag chos 'dir dad pa'ang rab dkon na //
K10D0145=D0847_H0100:518a-24: 'jug cing 'dzin pa smos kyang ci dgos te //
K10D0145=D0847_H0100:518a-25: gang dag de bzhin sgrub pa smos ci dgos //
K10D0145=D0847_H0100:518a-26: gang dag stong gsum ri dang rgya mtshor bcas //
K10D0145=D0847_H0100:518a-27: phyi ma'i bskal par mgo bos 'degs byed kyang //
K10D0145=D0847_H0100:518b-0: @518b chos 'dir dad pa'i bya dka' ci 'dra ba //
K10D0145=D0847_H0100:518b-1: de 'dra de ni de la yod ma yin //
K10D0145=D0847_H0100:518b-2: la las stong gsum rdul snyed sems can la //
K10D0145=D0847_H0100:518b-3: bde ba kun gyis bskal par bsnyen bkur yang //
K10D0145=D0847_H0100:518b-4: chos 'di dad pa'i bsod nams ci 'dra ba //
K10D0145=D0847_H0100:518b-5: bsod nams khyad par de 'dra de la med //
K10D0145=D0847_H0100:518b-6: la las zhing bcu ri dang rgya mtshor bcas //
K10D0145=D0847_H0100:518b-7: lag pa'i mthil du bskal par mkhar 'dzin kyang //
K10D0145=D0847_H0100:518b-8: chos 'dir dang pa'i bya dka' ci 'dra ba //
K10D0145=D0847_H0100:518b-9: de 'dra de ni de la yod ma yin //
K10D0145=D0847_H0100:518b-10: la las zhing bcu'i rdul snyed sems can la //
K10D0145=D0847_H0100:518b-11: bde ba kun gyis bskal par bsnyen bkur kyang //
K10D0145=D0847_H0100:518b-12: chos 'dir dad pa'i bsod nams ci 'dra ba //
K10D0145=D0847_H0100:518b-13: bsod nams khyad par de 'dra de la med //
K10D0145=D0847_H0100:518b-14: la las zhing bcu'i rdul snyed sangs rgyas rnams //
K10D0145=D0847_H0100:518b-15: bde ba kun gyis bskal par bsnyen bkur bas //
K10D0145=D0847_H0100:518b-16: gang gis chos kyi le'u 'di bzung byas pa //
K10D0145=D0847_H0100:518b-17: bsod nams de ni de bas khyad par 'phags //
K10D0145=D0847_H0100:518b-18: rnam thar de dag rab tu bstan ba'i tshe //
K10D0145=D0847_H0100:518b-19: phyogs bcu'i zhing rnams thams cad g-yos par gyur //
K10D0145=D0847_H0100:518b-20: bdud kyi gnas rnams mog mog byas gyur cing //
K10D0145=D0847_H0100:518b-21: sgra rab phyung bas ngan song rab tu zhi //
K10D0145=D0847_H0100:518b-22: phyogs bcu kun gyi mi yi sengge rnams //
K10D0145=D0847_H0100:518b-23: de dag kun gyis mngon par zhal bstan te //
K10D0145=D0847_H0100:518b-24: phyag brkyang mdzad nas yon tan mtha' yas pa //
K10D0145=D0847_H0100:518b-25: bzang po dpal gyi mgo la bzhag par gyur //
K10D0145=D0847_H0100:518b-26: phyag gi mthil gyis mgo la byug mdzad de //
K10D0145=D0847_H0100:518b-27: rnam thar 'di dag legs par bshad pa legs //
K10D0145=D0847_H0100:519a-0: @519a *// khyod kyis legs bstan rjes su nged dgyes zhes //
K10D0145=D0847_H0100:519a-1: sangs rgyas de dag kun gyis gsung brjod do //
K10D0145=D0847_H0100:519a-2: de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis tshigs su bcad pa
K10D0145=D0847_H0100:519a-3: bstan pa 'di dag bka' stsal nas cang mi gsung
K10D0145=D0847_H0100:519a-4: bar gyur to // de nas stong gsum gyi stong
K10D0145=D0847_H0100:519a-5: chen po'i 'jig rten gyi khams 'di na gang dag
K10D0145=D0847_H0100:519a-7: mi dang mi ma yin pa de dag thams cad
K10D0145=D0847_H0100:519a-8: kyis de bzhin gshegs pas 'di legs par bka' stsal
K10D0145=D0847_H0100:519a-9: to // kye ma de bzhin gshegs pas chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ba gnyis pa 'di mdzad do //
K10D0145=D0847_H0100:519a-10: chos bstan pa 'di sngon ma thos so //
K10D0145=D0847_H0100:519a-11: sems can gang dag chos kyi rnam grangs 'di rnyed
K10D0145=D0847_H0100:519a-12: par 'gyur ba de dag ni shin tu dkon te
K10D0145=D0847_H0100:519a-13: / sems can de dag ni dge ba'i rtsa ba ngan ngon dang ldan pa ma yin no //
K10D0145=D0847_H0100:519a-14: sems can de dag ni sangs rgyas mang po la bsnyen bkur byas pa yin no //
K10D0145=D0847_H0100:519a-15: sems can de dag ni lha dang bcas pa /
K10D0145=D0847_H0100:519a-17: tshangs pa dang bcas pa'i 'jig rten la mchod rten lta bur 'gyur te /
K10D0145=D0847_H0100:519a-19: bdud kyi ris kyi lha rnams sam /
K10D0145=D0847_H0100:519a-20: rab tu byung ba rnams sam /
K10D0145=D0847_H0100:519a-21: khyim na gnas pa rnams sam; de bzhin du rgyal po rnams sam /
K10D0145=D0847_H0100:519a-22: blon po chen po rnams sam /
K10D0145=D0847_H0100:519a-23: khyim bdag rnams kyis gtse bar mi nus so zhes ca co dang /
K10D0145=D0847_H0100:519b-0: de nas bcom ldan @519b 'das la tshe dang ldan pa rab 'byor kyis 'di skad ces gsol to //
K10D0145=D0847_H0100:519b-2: mdo sde dkon mchog 'di lta bu dag 'jig rten
K10D0145=D0847_H0100:519b-3: du 'byung ba ni rnyed par dka' ba lags te;
K10D0145=D0847_H0100:519b-4: 'on kyang de bzhin gshegs pa'i mthus chos 'di lta
K10D0145=D0847_H0100:519b-5: bu dag 'jig rten du byung zhing /
K10D0145=D0847_H0100:519b-6: de bzhin gshegs pa'i mthu nyid kyis sems can de
K10D0145=D0847_H0100:519b-7: dag gis kyang thos lags so; ;de nas bcom ldan
K10D0145=D0847_H0100:519b-8: 'das kyis ljags kyi dbang po phyung nas tshe dang
K10D0145=D0847_H0100:519b-9: ldan pa kun dga' bo la bka' stsal pa /
K10D0145=D0847_H0100:519b-11: khyod kyis chos kyi rnam grangs 'di zungs shig /
K10D0145=D0847_H0100:519b-15: de nas tshe dang ldan pa kun dga' bos bcom
K10D0145=D0847_H0100:519b-16: ldan 'das la lan gsum bskor ba byas te 'di
K10D0145=D0847_H0100:519b-19: bdag gis chos kyi rnam grangs 'di bzung lags te /
K10D0145=D0847_H0100:519b-20: slan chad mi bskyud par bgyid do //
K10D0145=D0847_H0100:519b-21: bcom ldan 'das kyis de skad ces bka' stsal nas
K10D0145=D0847_H0100:519b-22: thams cad dang ldan pa'i byang chub sems dpa'i 'khor
K10D0145=D0847_H0100:519b-23: dang / byang chub sems dpa' 'phags pa kun tu bzang po dang /
K10D0145=D0847_H0100:519b-24: 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa dang /
K10D0145=D0847_H0100:519b-25: tshe dang ldan pa sh'a radva ti'i bu dang /
K10D0145=D0847_H0100:519b-26: nyan thos chen po gzhan dag dang /
K10D0145=D0847_H0100:519b-30: dri zar bcas pa'i 'jig rten yi rang ste bcom
K10D0145=D0847_H0100:519b-31: ldan 'das kyis gsungs pa la mngon par bstod do
K10D0145=D0847_H0100:519b-32: // shin tu rgyas pa chen po'i mdo /
K10D0145=D0847_H0100:520a-2: dkon mchog ta la la zhes bya ba'i gzungs kyi chos kyi rnam grangs rdzogs so ////
K10D0145=D0847_H0100:520a-3: rgya gar gyi mkhan po su rendra bo dhi dang /
